	,"x4freetext":[" Five EJ-232Q and EJ-200 plastic scintillation"
		,"detectors measured the neutron yields from d + d"
		,"fusion reactions. Three of these detectors were"
		,"located 1.9 m from the fusion plasma, while the other"
		,"two were located 5 m from the plasma to increase the"
		,"dynamic range. Four additional NE213 liquid"
		,"scintillation detectors measured the angular"
		,"distribution of the fusion neutron emission at four"
		,"different angles."]
	}
      ]
